				<td colspan="2"><span>*ahem*
<br />

<br />
<b>STOP ***** TALKING ABOUT THE GODDAMNED AE NERF YA BASTARDS! IT'S DONE AND GONE AND GOOD-******-RIDDANCE TO IT!</b>
<br />

<br />
Deal. You're a bard damnit. <b>GROUP!!</b> Adapt. Do something other than AE kiting. Ooohhh I can't farm. Oooohhh I can't get teh phat expzorz. Ooohhh I'm such a lazy suckass. Ooohhh all I'm good for now is mana song and training. Boo ***** hoo man!
<br />

<br />
Shut up. Get over yourself. Move on. It's not like it's the end of the world man! You can still do other things to get teh phat expzorz. You can still do other things to farm greenies for tradeskill sh*t. You can still use other things to train people.
<br />

<br />
What is it you people want? Huh? Do you want to be known as the bitchyer monk-wannabe's? Cry babies? Lame asses? n00bz? We've been nerfed before. Harder. Rougher. Deeper. And what have we done? /whisper aaadddaaaappppttt. I'm sorry, what was that? Speak up man. I'm sorry, I said...&quot;<b>ADAPT!</b>&quot;
<br />

<br />
We're bards damnit. The single most adaptable class in the game. So you lost AE kiting. You're still useful. You can still get xp. You can still farm. You don't like it? Ya know what? Shut yer bitchin' and quit. Go to that nice pretty little screen that says &quot;Customer Information&quot; and go to &quot;Subscription&quot; and click the nice, big, pretty &quot;CANCEL&quot; button, and then shut up.
<br />

<br />
*counts off* 1) Grow up. 2) Adapt. 3) Shut yer bitchin'. 4) Cancel your subscription if you're that ****** depressed. 5) Shut up. 6) Die and go to h*ll.
<br />

<br />
Now just shut up!
<br />

<br />

<br />
Vulgarities removed --- Velvett.</span></td>
